Package: play.by.play
Title: Visualize NBA play by play data.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Henry", "Triebel", , "henry.triebel@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: NBA play-by-play shiny app that gets its information from the
    NBA stats page and can display the shot location, outcome, and player
    name per game in the order of the plays. This would enable users to
    have a more interactive and visually pleasing way to get an overview
    of the game.
